<div class="intro">
    <div class="team">
        <h1>Storyboarding</h1>
        <p>Writes the scripts and dialogue for the storylines, keyframes, and motion mechanics the animation requires. Writing and creative thinking abilities will be a crucial aspect of the team.</p>
        <h2>Hours per week: &#60 1 hour</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="team">
        <h1>Art Design</h1>
        <p>
            Handles visual design of characters, objects, backgrounds, animations, and 3D models/backgrounds, and video editing. Multiple visual design software will be utilized in this team’s work (Procreate, Procreate Dreams, Blender3D). A sub-group of this team is the Video Editing Team.
        </p>
        <h2>Hours per week: 1-3 hours</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="team">
        <h1>Sound Design</h1>
        <p>
            This team handles sound effects, music, and voice-acting for the animation series.
        </p>
        <h2>Hours per week: 1-2 hours</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="team">
        <h1>Web Design</h1>
        <p>
            This team creates a website that advertises, showcases, introduces, and explains the animation series, and makes it accessible to students and teachers. It also includes minigames for students to explore.
        </p>
        <h2>Hours per week: 1-2 hours</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="team">
        <h1>Outreach and Marketing</h1>
        <p>
            Handles the project communications, networking logistics, advertisement, and quote collection that will be incorporated into the game. Business and marketing skills are valued in this team.
        </p>
        <h2>Hours per week: &#60 1 hour</h2>
    </div>
</div>

